---
/* Hero.astro - Infused with Túlio's Pragmatic, High-Performance Vibe */
---
<div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight">
            Need a Backend That Runs Like Clockwork?
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-[var(--color-secondary)] mb-8 font-mono">
            I'm Túlio—A Pragmatic .NET Performance Engineer.
            <br />
            I build efficient, high-performance systems that don’t break under pressure.
            <br />
            <strong>Remote Only.</strong> Practical. Reliable. Results.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <a
              href="/resume"
              class="inline-block w-full md:w-auto bg-[var(--color-primary)] text-[var(--color-surface)] px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-[var(--color-primary)]/90 transition-colors font-mono text-sm"
            >
                View My Resume
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
